data.description: APPLE VALLEY CUSTOM HOME close to the Apple Valley Country Club and Golf Course. Gorgeous custom home located in the beautiful City of Apple Valley in a highly desirable golf course location. This single story features neutral tones, large primary suite with an enormous bathroom with soaker tub, walk in closets, a private office/study off the front entrance making this home a total package. Each area has been custom built to provide a special space. The large family room has a gorgeous fireplace. Take our word for it, you will love the family room off the gourmet kitchen with tons of windows allowing natural sunlight to flow throughout this home. Carpet floors, recessed lighting, granite counters,upgraded interior, fresh interior paint.  This is an amazing custom designs to satisfy the pickiest buyer and promises to amaze and delight. This huge property has a 1.6+ acres for all the toys, enjoy the sunsets as you have never enjoyed before! RV parking, and 3 car garage. Conveniently located near Golf course, Schools, dining, and easy access to the 15 freeway.
